<i>noun</i>: 평행선 [평행선], 양립 [양ː닙], 맞대응 [맏때응], 맞대결 [맏때결], 대치 [대ː치], 대적 [대ː적], 대면 [대ː면], 대립 [대ː립], 대결 [대ː결] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평행선 [평행선]</dt><br>
<dd>1. parallel lines</dd><br>
<dd>같은 평면 위에 있는 둘 이상의 나란히 곧은 선.</dd><br>
<dd>Two or more, straight lines that are placed side by side on the same plane.</dd><br>
<dd>2. confrontation</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 의견이나 주장 등이 합의를 이루지 못하고 계속 대립함.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The state of two or more opinions, arguments, etc., confronting each other.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>양립 [양ː닙]</dt><br>
<dd>1. coexistence; compatibility</dd><br>
<dd>두 가지가 동시에 따로 이루어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A simultaneous existence of two separate things.</dd><br>
<dd>2. confrontation</dd><br>
<dd>둘이 서로 굽히지 않고 맞섬.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of two persons or things opposing each other without any compromise.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>맞대응 [맏때응]</dt><br>
<dd>confrontation</dd><br>
<dd>상대의 위협적인 행동이나 태도에 맞서서 대응함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of standing up to an opponent's threatening behavior or attitude and dealing with it.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>맞대결 [맏때결]</dt><br>
<dd>confrontation</dd><br>
<dd>서로 맞서서 대결함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of two people facing and fighting each other.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>대치 [대ː치]</dt><br>
<dd>confrontation; standoff</dd><br>
<dd>서로 맞서서 버팀.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of standing firm against one another.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>대적 [대ː적]</dt><br>
<dd>confrontation; match</dd><br>
<dd>상대에게 맞서 싸움.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of fighting against one's opponent.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>대면 [대ː면]</dt><br>
<dd>interview; meeting in person; confrontation</dd><br>
<dd>직접 얼굴을 보며 만남.</dd><br>
<dd>Meeting someone in person.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>대립 [대ː립]</dt><br>
<dd>opposition; confrontation; conflict</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 의견, 입장이 서로 반대되거나 맞지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>A thought, opinion, or stance being opposing or not consistent.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>대결 [대ː결]</dt><br>
<dd>contest; confrontation</dd><br>
<dd>둘이 서로 맞서서 우열이나 승패를 가림.</dd><br>
<dd>Two persons or parties facing each other and competing to excel or to win.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>